Opinions, including mine, on external companies are often unsure or mixed. However, I do know the Roblox platform is like nothing else with its equality of opportunity.

Success comes down to execution, and execution requires understanding of how this platform works.

It almost seems as if Roblox has been light years ahead of us looking at all of this.

Think what you want about the outside companies, but the way the Roblox platform works puts an unignorable emphasis on the individual creator. Key word here, native.
